text: David Frank Kustoff ( ; born October 8, 1966) is an American politician and attorney. He has been the United States representative from since 2017. From 2006 to 2008, Kustoff was a United States Attorney for the Western District of Tennessee. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official U.S. House website *Official campaign website * Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Memphis, Tennessee Category:Lawyers from Memphis, Tennessee Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:United States representatives from Tennessee
